General Information

Vitamin C is great for Immune support Contains Vitamin C which is an Antioxidant. Daily intake at recommended dose might prevent deficiency of Vitamin C. Assists in maintenance of general health and well being.

Warnings

Always read the label; take only as directed. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. Not to be used in children under two years of age without medical advice.

Immune Support

Ingredients

Each Gummy contains: Ascorbic acid (Vitamin C) 64 mg

Directions
